Recipe "Bubble Sort"
    Serves 1

    Ingredients
        1 list arr
        1 number n

    Method
        Preheat oven to 200 degrees.

        Take "arr" and "n".
        Combine "arr" and "n" into a mixing bowl.

        Sift "arr" and "n" together using a sieve.

        Fold "arr" into a sorted order using a spatula.

        Pour mixture into a baking dish.

        Bake for n minutes.

        Serve hot.

    Enjoy "Bubble Sort"!
